Define type of Car object to manage, which elements should be visible in shop and which are only helper objects to take advantage of data inheritance.

Place where optional additional settings can go. 
These settings need to be taken care about by the implementation. They are not considered by the framework by default.

children.html:
Preconditions are applied to the product list without being shown at the filters list in the frontend. Therefore preconditions cannot be changed by the user in the frontend.
In order to filter for specific value use the pre select attribute in the entries.

children.name: filtersInheritance
children.title: inherit Filters

children.name: Layout
children.html:
OnlineShopTaxClass as definition for tax calculation within ecommerce frameworks price systems. Products price system decides which TaxClass to take and does the tax calculation based on it. 

Tax Entry Combination Type defines how tax entry rates are combined: 
  • Combine: Sum up all tax rates and calculates tax amount afterwards.
  • One After Another: For each tax rate calculate tax amount, add it to total sum and then calculate tax amount for next tax rate based on new total sum.

Actual tokens are available in additional tab 'Voucher Service'
